{"tid":636563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打賭由羅湖行至尖咀　網民完成「萬里長征」獲讚真漢子","createTime":"2018-04-21T04:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T00:25:58.000Z","uid":81228,"like":17,"dislike":246,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"400c66d042860ab84cad8252d59c1a180f277387","tid":636563,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"打賭由羅湖行至尖咀　網民完成「萬里長征」獲讚真漢子<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180421/_2018042111012167468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180421%2F_2018042111012167468.jpg&h=a276d3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三人由羅湖行至尖咀，完成「萬里長征」。網上圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180421/_2018042111012059944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180421%2F_2018042111012059944.jpg&h=d6af45a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三人完成「萬里長征」，與朋友合照。網上圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180421/_2018042111012119696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180421%2F_2018042111012119696.jpg&h=4a5e1cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180421/_2018042111025179241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180421%2F_2018042111025179241.jpg&h=23b23790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三人由下午行到夜晚，筋疲力盡。網上圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180421/_2018042111012292795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180421%2F_2018042111012292795.jpg&h=b3f4ed54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡世界充滿謊言，不少人「講吓就算」無需負責任。近日網上就出現三名「找數真漢子」，與朋友打賭於於Facebook群組開post，24小時內有500個Like及800個留言，就會穿和尚服由羅湖行路出尖沙咀，不少網民起初「睇死」會走數，但三名真漢子昨日「找數」，用一日時間由新界北行路出尖沙咀，獲網民激讚真男人。<br />\n<br />\n事源有網民日前於Facebook專頁「巴打絲打」發文，指其三個朋友不相信會在24小時內有500個Like及800個留言，否則會直播穿和尚服由羅湖行路出尖沙咀。網民隨即發揮力量，不足24小時已超額完成，吸引逾7000個Like以及近3500個留言，網民紛紛起哄叫三人「找數」。<br />\n<br />\n而三人果真「找數」，三人昨午一時許身穿和尚服裝由羅湖出發，沿途直播「找數」過程，用約二個多小時才由羅湖行至大埔，沿途有網民攜同食水和乾糧等到場為三名「和尚」打氣，因路程遙遠，三人最終於昨夜11時至今晨時份，抵達尖沙咀碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n三名「和尚」的「萬里長征」感動不少網民，除了是「找數真漢子外」，更體現年輕人的活力和無比毅力，「講得出做得到值得敬重」、「真心配服同欣賞呢幾位年青人，趁後生去玩得wild啲，大家開心啲，社會先小啲怨氣」、「其實開頭諗住佢地行唔晒甚至走數，但見佢地一步一步，很努力咁行，完成個旅程，真係有啲感動」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1196316/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1196316%2F&d=sQdzBtL1UQ3B5MZCQ%2FJm3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=885d9279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1196316%2F&h=c43d4f90\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1196316/</a>"},{"pid":"b26c3636f11a9a5f0acaee83f1b926dae8e27f87","tid":636563,"uid":137912,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"82029027c8bd6fbf4e095c4f823e11b34e755ba0","tid":636563,"uid":41524,"like":260,"dislike":3,"score":257,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"「其實開頭諗住佢地行唔晒甚至走數，但見佢地一步一步，很努力咁行，完成個旅程，真係有啲感動」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行一日路咋喎...........<br />\n睇住日日返體力勞動工既人會唔會喊到死老豆咁"},{"pid":"153911c6d7194b87409595c30a4dc8cba382aaa1","tid":636563,"uid":83217,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"82029027c8bd6fbf4e095c4f823e11b34e755ba0","tid":636563,"uid":41524,"like":260,"dislike":3,"score":257,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:04:5